SystemConfig NEWS
=================

0.2 (Etoile 0.4)
----------------

- Support for system-related infos taken from AboutEtoileEntry
- Several header include fixes to compile on more platforms
- Preliminary X11 keyboard configuration such as delay, repeat... (Nyap Hong Koh)
- libacpi battery monitor support but disabled by default, see INSTALL (Lennart 
  Melzer)
- APM-based battery monitor support for Linux, FreeBSD and OpenBSD (Yen-Ju Chen 
  & David Chisnall)


0.1 (Etoile 0.2)
----------------

- First release.
